headline: OpenTable Launches Gen-AI Powered Concierge to Arm Diners with Instant Insights for its 60,000+ Global Restaurants
summary: OpenTable, a global leader in restaurant tech, today debuted 'Concierge,' a generative AI-powered assistant designed to give diners instant insights into more than 60,000 restaurants on its network. The launch deepens OpenTable's continued investment in AI to support restaurants and diners.
